\end{definition}

\lstinline|\cref{def: strange}| will be displayed as: \cref{def: strange}.

After using \lstinline|\UseLanguage{French}|, a theorem will be displayed as:

\UseLanguage{French}
\begin{theorem}[Inutile]\label{thm}
